  [ Colin Ian King ]
  * Makefile: bump version
  * mincore: fix build for GNU/HURD; make it a no-op
  * stress-mlock: don't build in munlockall for GNU/HURD
  * stress-mlock: don't build in mlockall, munlockall for GNU/HURD
